Package org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.productmanager.productcatalog

Enum Class ProductFolderDefinition

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<ProductFolderDefinition>
org.odpi.openmetadata.adapters.connectors.productmanager.productcatalog.ProductFolderDefinition
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<ProductFolderDefinition>, Constable
public enum ProductFolderDefinition extends Enum<ProductFolderDefinition>
The ProductFolderDefinition describes the different folders in the Open Metadata Product Catalog. This includes the top-level folder for the whole catalog.
